<!-- ★ EVERY STAGE HAS A PURPOSE — Animated Filtration Pipeline ★ -->
<div class="stages-bg sec" id="stages">
<div class="container">
<div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:52px" class="reveal">
<div class="lbl" style="color:var(--gold)">SEQUENTIAL STRESS-REMOVAL ARCHITECTURE</div>
<h2>Every Stage Has a Purpose</h2>
<p style="color:var(--mut);max-width:620px;margin:12px auto 0;font-size:17px">This isn't random layering. Each stage targets a specific class of threat — in the exact order your water needs it. Watch how your shower water transforms.</p>
</div>

<!-- Filter Cross-Section Diagram Placeholder -->
<div class="reveal" style="margin-bottom:40px;border:2px dashed rgba(176,134,66,.4);border-radius:24px;padding:40px 28px;background:rgba(176,134,66,.04);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:12px;text-align:center;max-width:700px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto">
  <span style="font-size:44px;opacity:.4">🔬</span>
  <span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em">15-Stage Filter Cross-Section Diagram</span>
  <span style="font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);opacity:.5">Upload cutaway illustration showing all 15 filtration layers</span>
</div>

<!-- ANIMATED WATER FLOW INDICATOR -->
<div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:36px" class="reveal">
<div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:16px;background:var(--wh);border:1px solid var(--bdr);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)">
<div style="position:relative;width:24px;height:24px">
<div style="position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:50%;background:var(--red);opacity:.15;animation:pulseGold 2s infinite"></div>
<div style="position:absolute;inset:4px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--red)"></div>
</div>
<span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--red)">Unfiltered tap water enters</span>
<span style="font-size:20px">→</span>
<span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--mut)">15 stages process every drop</span>
<span style="font-size:20px">→</span>
<div style="position:relative;width:24px;height:24px">
<div style="position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:50%;background:var(--sage);opacity:.15;animation:pulseGold 2s infinite"></div>
<div style="position:absolute;inset:4px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--sage)"></div>
</div>
<span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--sage)">Clean, vitamin-enriched water out</span>
</div>
</div>

<div class="stage-pipeline" id="stagePipeline">

<!-- STAGE 1 -->
<div class="stage-item reveal" data-stage="1">
<div class="stage-num-wrap"><div class="stage-num" style="background:var(--gold)">1
<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64"><circle cx="32" cy="32" r="30" stroke="var(--gold)" opacity=".3"/></svg></div></div>
<div class="stage-body">
<div class="stage-role" style="color:var(--gold)">The First Line of Defense</div>
<h4>Sediment Pre-Filter</h4>
<p>Captures rust flakes, sand, pipe debris, and particulate matter before they reach your skin. Post-menopausal skin has weaker lipid cohesion — physical particles create micro-friction and barrier disruption on already-thinned tissue.</p>
<div class="stage-removes"><span style="background:var(--gold2);color:var(--gold)">✓ Rust &amp; sediment</span><span style="background:var(--gold2);color:var(--gold)">✓ Pipe debris</span><span style="background:var(--gold2);color:var(--gold)">✓ Micro-particles</span></div>
</div></div>

<div class="stage-connector"><div class="drop"></div></div>

<!-- STAGE 2 -->
<div class="stage-item reveal" data-stage="2">
<div class="stage-num-wrap"><div class="stage-num" style="background:var(--sage)">2
<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64"><circle cx="32" cy="32" r="30" stroke="var(--sage)" opacity=".3"/></svg></div></div>
<div class="stage-body">
<div class="stage-role" style="color:var(--sage)">The Rapid Neutralizer</div>
<h4>Calcium Sulfite</h4>
<p>Converts free chlorine into harmless chloride salts — <em>instantly</em>, even in hot water. This matters because hot showers increase chlorine volatility (you're breathing it as gas) and skin permeability. Chlorine oxidizes surface lipids, strips fatty acids, and triggers the oxidative stress that accelerates collagen breakdown.</p>
<div class="stage-removes"><span style="background:var(--sage3);color:var(--sage)">✓ Free chlorine</span><span style="background:var(--sage3);color:var(--sage)">✓ Chlorine gas (steam)</span><span style="background:var(--sage3);color:var(--sage)">✓ Lipid oxidation</span></div>
</div></div>

<div class="stage-connector"><div class="drop"></div></div>

<!-- STAGE 3 -->
<div class="stage-item reveal" data-stage="3">
<div class="stage-num-wrap"><div class="stage-num" style="background:#6366F1">3
<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64"><circle cx="32" cy="32" r="30" stroke="#6366F1" opacity=".3"/></svg></div></div>
<div class="stage-body">
<div class="stage-role" style="color:#6366F1">The Antioxidant Shield</div>
<h4>Vitamin C — Sodium Ascorbate</h4>
<p>Neutralizes residual disinfectants that calcium sulfite missed, including chloramines. But the real story: after estrogen declines, your body's internal antioxidant capacity drops. Vitamin C in filtration provides <em>environmental antioxidant defense</em> — reducing oxidative load before it contacts your skin. Applied chemistry, not wellness marketing.</p>
<div class="stage-removes"><span style="background:rgba(99,102,241,.06);color:#6366F1">✓ Chloramines</span><span style="background:rgba(99,102,241,.06);color:#6366F1">✓ Oxidative stress</span><span style="background:rgba(99,102,241,.06);color:#6366F1">✓ Free radicals</span></div>
</div></div>

<div class="stage-connector"><div class="drop"></div></div>

<!-- STAGE 4 -->
<div class="stage-item reveal" data-stage="4">
<div class="stage-num-wrap"><div class="stage-num" style="background:var(--navy)">4
<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64"><circle cx="32" cy="32" r="30" stroke="var(--navy)" opacity=".3"/></svg></div></div>
<div class="stage-body">
<div class="stage-role" style="color:var(--navy)">The Heavy Metal Shield</div>
<h4>KDF-55 Copper-Zinc Media</h4>
<p>Electrochemical redox reactions convert dissolved heavy metals (lead, mercury, nickel) into insoluble forms and suppress bacterial biofilm growth. Heavy metals catalyze oxidative stress — the same force accelerating collagen breakdown and follicular miniaturization. This stage protects both skin structural proteins and follicle integrity.</p>
<div class="stage-removes"><span style="background:rgba(27,58,75,.06);color:var(--navy)">✓ Lead &amp; mercury</span><span style="background:rgba(27,58,75,.06);color:var(--navy)">✓ Nickel &amp; copper</span><span style="background:rgba(27,58,75,.06);color:var(--navy)">✓ Bacteria</span></div>
</div></div>

<div class="stage-connector"><div class="drop"></div></div>

<!-- STAGE 5 -->
<div class="stage-item reveal" data-stage="5">
<div class="stage-num-wrap"><div class="stage-num" style="background:var(--rose)">5
<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64"><circle cx="32" cy="32" r="30" stroke="var(--rose)" opacity=".3"/></svg></div></div>
<div class="stage-body">
<div class="stage-role" style="color:var(--rose)">The Deep Clean Finish</div>
<h4>Catalytic Activated Carbon</h4>
<p>Engineered with enhanced surface area to break down chloramines — which standard carbon struggles with. Also adsorbs VOCs, PFAS traces, and organic contaminants. Chloramines are more stable, harder to remove, and more persistent irritants than chlorine. This final stage ensures the lowest possible chemical load reaches your skin.</p>
<div class="stage-removes"><span style="background:var(--rose3);color:var(--rose)">✓ Chloramines</span><span style="background:var(--rose3);color:var(--rose)">✓ VOCs &amp; PFAS</span><span style="background:var(--rose3);color:var(--rose)">✓ Organic compounds</span></div>
</div></div>

</div><!-- end pipeline -->

<!-- RESULT INDICATOR -->
<div style="text-align:center;margin-top:40px" class="reveal">
<div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:18px 32px;border-radius:20px;background:var(--wh);border:2px solid var(--sage);box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(94,138,106,.12)">
<div style="font-size:32px">✨</div>
<div style="text-align:left"><div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--sage)">Water exits clean, vitamin-enriched &amp; pH-balanced</div>
<div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--mut)">95%+ contaminants removed · Vitamins A, C &amp; E infused · Ready for compromised skin</div></div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- WHY 5 STAGES = 15 -->
<div style="text-align:center;margin-top:28px" class="reveal">
<p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--mut);max-width:580px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.7"><strong style="color:var(--ink)">Why do we say "15-stage"?</strong> Each of these 5 primary media groups contains 3 sub-layers of varying granularity, optimized for contact time at shower flow rates. 5 groups × 3 sub-layers = 15 sequential filtration stages.</p>
</div>

</div></div>


